{"tid":2264892,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【倒數階段】民調：拜登在全國支持率持續領先特朗普","createTime":"2020-10-31T04:22:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T04:22:41.000Z","uid":278587,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e6d483e3c26904660a78b9aea5c97abf1bff6e68","tid":2264892,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T04:22:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=411000&amp;catCode=123&amp;topicId=1039\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D411000%26catCode%3D123%26topicId%3D1039&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdkVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=85224bda\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D411000%26catCode%3D123%26topicId%3D1039&h=d9359fb0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=411000&amp;catCode=123&amp;topicId=1039</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】距離美國大選日不足一周，逾8000萬人已投票。民意調查顯示，拜登在全國支持度持續領先特朗普。<br />\n<br />\n美國民意調查分析網站以及英國《衛報》分別綜合多項民調顯示，截至周三，拜登在全國的平均支持度，領先特朗普約9個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n搖擺州份方面，根據《衛報》的數據，二人在剛到訪的佛羅里達勢均力敵；在兵家必爭的中西部賓夕法尼亞和密歇根州，拜登則領先5至7個百分點；被視為大選風向標的俄亥俄州，特朗普保持近2個百分點優勢。"}]}